-- Merrill Lynch Sued by New York Over Mortgage-Linked Pension Fund Losses
-- Bob Van Voris
-- 2010-07-22T14:10:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-22/merrill-lynch-sued-by-new-york-over-mortgage-linked-pension-fund-losses.html

          
          
             Merrill Lynch & Co. was sued by New
York’s comptroller over losses to the state’s retirement fund
tied to collateralized debt obligations and residential
mortgage-backed securities.  
